Tim Thomerson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Thomerson 0 Joseph Timothy "Tim" Thomerson (born April 8, 1946) is an American actor and comedian.Thomerson is most famous for his role as Jack Deth in the Trancers film series and is renowned for his work in numerous low-budget movies and his comedic television roles.
